Interface OperatingSystemRoot

All Known Implementing Classes:
OperatingSystemRootImpl
public interface OperatingSystemRoot

A representation of the model object 'Operating System Root'.

The following features are supported:

  • Mixed
  • XMLNS Prefix Map
  • XSI Schema Location
  • Capability Aix Local Group
